summary";s:135:"Yoast&#039;s all in one SEO solution for your WordPress blog: SEO titles, meta descriptions, XML sitemaps, breadcrumbs &#38; much more.";}i:13;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:46:"b0rjara on "Goto Outbound Links and Analytics"";s:4:"link";s:81:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/goto-outbound-links-and-analytics/#post-22529";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Fri, 26 Nov 2010 16:00:14 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:7:"b0rjara";}s:4:"guid";s:42:"22529@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:146:"Lets you create and analyze goto links such as <a href="http://www.yoursite.com/goto/link/" rel="nofollow">http://www.yoursite.com/goto/link/</a>.";s:7:"summary";s:146:"Lets you create and analyze goto links such as <a href="http://www.yoursite.com/goto/link/" rel="nofollow">http://www.yoursite.com/goto/link/</a>.";}i:14;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:26:"José Conti on "WangGuard"";s:4:"link";s:57:"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wangguard/#post-24693";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Thu, 24 Feb 2011 19:50:57 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:11:"José Conti";}s:4:"guid";s:42:"24693@http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/";s:11:"description";s:147:"WangGuard checks your registered users against WangGuard web service to avoid Sploggers, is fully WordPress,WordPress MU and BuddyPress compatible.";s:7:"summary";s:147:"WangGuard checks your registered users against WangGuard web service to avoid Sploggers, is fully WordPress,WordPress MU and BuddyPress compatible.";}}s:7:"channel";a:7:{s:5:"title";s:42:"WordPress Plugins ', 'no'),
