Theme Releases for 4/3";s:4:"guid";s:40:"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/?p=9846";s:4:"link";s:73:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~3/Y0aBq9ZPnMU/";s:11:"description";s:1652:"<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9847" title="bazanoclegowa" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/bazanoclegowa.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/baza-noclegowa"><strong>Baza Noclegowa</strong></a> is a clean, clear, and light theme for blogs, corporate websites, and big portals as well.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9848" title="citrus" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/citrus.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://emptynestthemes.emptynestheritage.com/?p=580"><strong>Citrus</strong></a> is based on greens and oranges, and available in narrow (2 column), medium (2 column), and wide (3 column) varieties.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9849" title="myphoto" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/myphoto.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.wpexplorer.com/myphoto-wordpress-theme.html"><strong>MyPhoto</strong></a> is a very clean and elegant theme created specifically with photography, portfolio, and other gallery type sites in mind.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9850" title="spaceweapons" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/spaceweapons.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://stockable.net/space-weapons/"><strong>Space Weapons</strong></a> is a two column theme, perfect for personal blogs and space enthusiasts.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/Y0aBq9ZPnMU" height="1" width="1" />";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Sun, 03 Apr 2011 13:00:31 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:10:"James Huff";}s:7:"summary";s:1652:"<p><img class=